replies.body:
How about you simply make an alchemist champion?
All {{champion:27}} mains love him so why take that away?

R.I.P {{champion:82}} {{champion:43}}

To be exact it is a quest between {{champion:22}} {{champion:127}} {{champion:113}} 
At some point of the game the quest will appear if 2 of these champs are in opposing teams. Killing the other one makes you become the "queen of freljord" and you get a small crown above of your champ model. Has no in game effect, though.

Just for the people who always wanted to be a queen.
